name: Gundou Misuzu | Tomo-chan is a girl!

  • trigger word is just for her basic hair style, for other styles use their respective trigger word

  • Trained with 250 screenshots from the anime, manually cropped and taged

  • Hires fix or inpaint for detailed eyes.

  • has trouble with some hair styles some times (*)

  • some occasions generates realistic styles regardless of the model used
